---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "../components/container.astro";
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service">
  <Container>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-14 mb-20">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-3">
        <span class="text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm font-bold">Compliance</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight text-slate-800">
          Terms of Service
        </h1>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Last Updated: February 24, 2025</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 prose prose-lg max-w-none prose-headings:text-slate-800 prose-p:text-slate-600 border-t border-slate-100 pt-10">
        <h3>1. Acceptance of Terms</h3>
        <p>By accessing <strong>AutoChina.org</strong>, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please discontinue your use of the Website immediately.</p>

        <h3>2. Intellectual Property Rights</h3>
        <p>All content, including but not limited to strategic reports, data visualizations, and industry analysis, is the property of <strong>AutoChina Intelligence</strong>.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Permitted Use:</strong> You may quote short excerpts of our content provided that clear attribution is given with a backlink to the original source.</li>
          <li><strong>Prohibited Use:</strong> Systematic scraping or redistribution of our reports for commercial purposes is strictly prohibited.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>3. Nature of Intelligence</h3>
        <p>The content provided on this Website is for <strong>informational and research purposes only</strong>. We do not provide financial, legal, or investment advice. Market conditions are subject to rapid change; we do not guarantee the absolute accuracy of the information provided.</p>

        <h3>4. Limitation of Liability</h3>
        <p>AutoChina Intelligence shall not be liable for any direct or indirect damages arising from your use of the Website or reliance on our intelligence reports.</p>

        <p class="mt-10 text-sm text-slate-400 italic">Inquiries: contact@autochina.org</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>
